data.title: About
data.meta_description: The KSRC, a chartered affiliate of the American Association for Respiratory Care (AARC), is a not-for-profit organization established to serve the professional needs of the respiratory profession
data.text:
The KSRC is comprised of respiratory therapists representing every region of Kentucky. As the Kentucky affiliate of the American Association for Respiratory Care (AARC), your membership to the AARC means you are a member of the KSRC. The KSRC's goal is to serve, advocate and advance the respiratory care profession in the state of Kentucky.

The Kentucky Society for Respiratory Care (KSRC), a chartered affiliate of the American Association for Respiratory Care (AARC), is a not-for-profit organization established to serve the professional needs of the respiratory profession and its practitioners, and support that profession's ability to meet the needs of its patients.
